title: [Gyldemar Forest, Stagnant Pool]
description: Sickly green scum covers the surface of the pool, parting temporarily with each intrusion.  Decaying leaves form a fittingly disgusting border to the pool.

Sickly green scum covers the surface of the pool, parting temporarily with each intrusion.  Decaying leaves form a fittingly disgusting border to the pool.  The nighttime darkness does little to hide the disgusting sight.
